---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/10/17	(0.3.5)

* Some minor bugfixes and updates for kanotix-update and -check-knofig

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/10/15	(0.3.4)

* Fixed UID-1000-problem in kanotix-update
* Added /etc/iftab to rescue-list in kanotix-update
* Some other minor bugfixes and updates

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/10/11	(0.3.3)

* Fixed Chown-Bug in kanotix-update
* Fixed Typo ("passwort" instead of "password")

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/10/04	(0.3.2)

* Added "Force Installation"-Checkbox
* Removed "Install Bootloader"-Checkbox

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/28	(0.3.1)

* Changed kanotix-update, now with better user/group-update
* Added time-statistics to kanotix-update
* fixdevlist-Patch included

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/25	(0.3.0)

* Added Bootloader-Recovery
* Main-Window is hidden now when Partition-Manager is active

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/22	(0.2.9)

* Added Recovery-Tools

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/16	(0.2.8)

* Check, if Root-Partition is selected
* Ask the user to do "rebuildfstab" after changing the Partition-Table

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/13	(0.2.7)

* Some changes on kanotix-update-Script

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/11	(0.2.6)

* Now saving old Package-List in /root/ (update-installation)
* Some bugfixes

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/09	(0.2.5)

* Improved German i18n
* Added some Warnings (e.g. for Partition-Resizing)
* Some bugfixes in kanotix-update
* Added knxinstaller-script, a wrapper for kanotix-installer's ni-mode

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/07	(0.2.4)

* Some Bugfixes

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/06	(0.2.3)

* Added Update-Mode

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/09/04	(0.2.2)

* Changed QTParted-Wrapper (using ExitCode of Processes now)
* Added ReiserFS-Wrapper

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/08/20	(0.2.1)

* Fixed bug with escaping $ to \$ in encrypted Passwords
* Changed text "/root/.knofig" to "~/.knofig"
* Added parsing of an existing .knofig
* Update of QTParted-Sources to 0.4.5

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/08/05	(0.2)

* Added an own Partition-Manager (based on QTParted 0.4.4)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/08/02	(0.1.2)

* "--non-interactive"-Mode will be started REALLY!

  ####################################
  ##### BE CAREFUL WHILE TESTING! ####
  ####################################

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/08/02	(0.1.1)

* "Network"-Tab for setting Hostname
* Creating .knofig in /tmp and move it to /root later by sudo mv ...


---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2005/08/01	(0.1)

* First release
* Check if partition is swap now case-insensitive

